    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那这个流程的起点是WAITING_FILE状态吗？还是直接从PatientRecords系统进入？另外，什么情况下会触发状态转换？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
