    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，起点是WAITING_FILE。当PatientRecords检测到有待上传文件时，就进入WAITING_FILE状态；如果没有文件，则直接进入SENDING状态。这两个分支都要画出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WAITING_FILE",
        "SENDING",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Presenza di file da caricare",
        "No file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经添加了从PatientRecords到WAITING_FILE和SENDING的两条分支，标注了触发条件。接下来SENDING之后是什么状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SENDING",
        "REGISTERED",
        "Creata entità su SEND"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SENDING之后进入REGISTERED状态，表示在SEND服务上创建了实体。然后REGISTERED有两个出口：如果有文件就先到UPLOADED，再到COMPLETE；如果没有文件就直接到COMPLETE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REGISTERED",
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE",
        "File caricati",
        "No file da caricare"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，UPLOADED只出现在有文件上传的路径上，然后UPLOADED再到COMPLETE。那COMPLETE之后呢？流程结束了吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "UPLOADED",
        "COMPLETE"
